Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:01.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.36,0:00:02.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Little Cotton Candy here was right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:05.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And, if I do say so myselfâ€¦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:09.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This town is not a nice place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:12.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For little fillies all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:15.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There are lots of twists and corners
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:18.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That could lead to the unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:21.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Let me guide your way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:24.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I'll be sure to help you through
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You could really use a friend out here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:31.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And luckily for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:34.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm the friend that you need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:37.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When you're lost and don't know what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:40.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm your pal, your amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:43.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Useful and resourceful, too
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:46.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And my help, you'll concede
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:49.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is a plus, guaranteed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:50.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You can call and I'll come running
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just follow my lead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm the friend you need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:57.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Quite a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.37,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He's a friend indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:02.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You need a bud to spot the danger
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:03.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A pal to stop the creep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:06.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A chum and not a stranger to assist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:08.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You need a bro who is cunning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:09.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That can help you take the leap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:11.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A friend who knows what's lying in the mist
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:14.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Don't fear these darkened alleys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:17.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They're scary, yes, I know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:20.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Why, you could use a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:23.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To protect you wherever you go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:26.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And such a dazzling beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:28.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Covered in dirt and muck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:31.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But now your fate is changing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:34.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now you are in luck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:37.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm the friend that you need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When you're lost and don't know what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:42.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm your pal, your amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:45.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Lookin' out for friends like you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:48.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And my help, you'll concede
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is a plus, guaranteed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:52.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just call and I'll come running
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:54.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We'll say it's agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Here! Tell Verko: "My place, twenty minutes"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:03.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I've got something that will magically erase all my debt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:09.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm the friend you need
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He's a friend indeed